 Weber die »objektiven« Ursachen und die schweren bankpolitischen Fehler, die zum Zusammenbruch der Bank führten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aBanks and bankingzAustriaxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aCreditanstalt-Gesetz, Weltwirtschaftskrise, Rothschild.1 aAndrosch, Hannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMatis, Herbert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2016z9783110485189oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205201823423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205201823.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016